law.history: Repealed 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 186, Art. V, sec. 2, effective March 25, 1960. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 218, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 4281c-5, 4281c-6, 4281c-10.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Who to pay tax and affix tax stamps.
